<item>
            <title>[LU-3986] eliminate redundant kernel config files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3986</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Due to a historical artifact in the lbuild script kernel config files for sles kernel builds are duplicated under both names kernel-...&lt;del&gt;x86_46.config and kernel&lt;/del&gt;...-x86_64-default.config.  This is really unnecessary and is only done due to a quirk in the existing script.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will push a patch to clean this up.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
